description:
If you want to support my channel please don’t donate to me, please donate to a charity that impressed me greatly when I saw it in operation in Borneo. It's an expanding clinic called ASRI which offers cheap health care to villagers in exchange for an end to deforestation of the rainforest that surrounds them. 

You can make a donation by bank transfer to Indonesia here…
http://www.alamsehatlestari.org/donate/

…or to the USA here:
https://healthinharmony.org/donate/

To find out more, check out this article written in 2012…
https://psmag.com/social-justice/save...

…or listen to the 30-minute package I did for the BBC in 2016:
http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08hnly0

   Here are the sources for my video:

0:00 “What They Haven't Told You about Climate Change” by PragerU
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RkdbSxyXftc&t=2s

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FI3ZVre__Xg

7:36 --  “What They Haven't Told You about Climate Change” by PragerU
